HEADWORD: Drawboy
<hw>Draw"boy`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Weaving)</fld>
<def>A boy who operates the harness cords of a hand loom; also, a part
of power loom that performs the same office.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Drawbridge</ent>⟦br⟧
